queries.sql: SELECT `E`.*, `U`.*, `CV`.`description`, GROUP_CONCAT(P.idProfil) as idProfil, GROUP_CONCAT(P.intitule SEPARATOR " - ") as profils FROM `etudiant` AS `E` JOIN `utilisateur` AS `U` ON `U`.`idUtilisateur` = `E`.`idUtilisateur` LEFT JOIN `cv` AS `CV` ON `E`.`idCV` = `CV`.`idCV` LEFT JOIN `profil_cv` AS `PCV` ON `PCV`.`idCV` = `CV`.`idCV` JOIN `profil` AS `P` ON `P`.`idProfil` = `PCV`.`idProfil` WHERE `E`.`idEtudiant` = ('2') LIMIT 1
